item.title: Help plzz help!
item.dc:creator: @mr_pker01 mr pker01
item.description:
@mr_pker01 wrote:

Go www.canyouseeme.org then type 43594 and click “CHECK” then when it says successful ur server is online . Go to ur client files and open client.java search “Server =” change the numbers or ip into ur No-ip address, then save then compile . Remove the .java files then upload it at any uploading site but i suggest www.mediafire.com tell ur friends to download it then tell them to login (Make sure ur source is open)

If still not work, just turn off ur anti-virus and allow incoming connections in ur firewall
